<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلَا يَصِحُّ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- صَوْمُ أَيَّامِ التَّشْرِيقِ، إِلَّا عَنْ دَمِ مُتْعَةٍ أَوْ قِرَانٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا صَوْمُ عِيدٍ مُطْلَقًا، وَيَحْرُمُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمَنْ دَخَلَ فِي تَطَوُّعٍ غَيْرِ حَجٍّ أَوْ عُمْرَةٍ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- لَمْ يَجِبْ إِتْمَامُهُ، وَيُسَنُّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ فَسَدَ:</span> فَلَا قَضَاءَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَيَجِبُ إِتْمَامُ فَرْضٍ مُطْلَقًا، وَلَوْ مُوَسَّعًا؛ كَصَلَاةٍ، وَقَضَاءِ رَمَضَانَ، وَنَذْرٍ مُطْلَقٍ، وَكَفَّارَةٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ بَطَلَ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- فَلَا مَزِيدَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَلَا كَفَّارَةَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَفْضَلُ الأَيَّامِ:</span> يَوْمُ الجُمُعَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَفْضَلُ اللَّيَالِي:</span> لَيْلَةُ القَدْرِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَتُطْلَبُ فِي العَشْرِ الأَخِيرِ مِنْ رَمَضَانَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَأَوْتَارُهُ آكَدُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَأَرْجَاهَا سَابِعُهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>